Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.69,0:00:37.96,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}教室のドアくぐると
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.69,0:00:37.96,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(300,300)}跨進教室大門
